System
------

    melt of 100 chains of 8 atoms.

    Requires a version of mdSim compiled with angles (-a) and
    dihedrals (-d) enabled.

Usage
-----

Serial NVE MD simulation:

    mdSim -e -p param.nve -c commands

Serial NVT MD simulation:

    mdSim_a_d -e -p param.nvt -c commands

Restarting and extending previous simulation

    mdSim -e -r restart -c commands.rst
